title="Proposition">proposition</fr:link>. In other words, we must show that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x,y:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x,y:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x,y:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x,y:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}\mathsf {isTruncated}\,\mathopen {}\left ({n-1}\right )\mathclose {}\,A]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link
